Name: Achievements printer
About the game: Achievement printer is simple basketball game. You need swipe the ball towards the hoop to score Here some game features - 2999 Achievements - Nice sound and graphics - Simple gameplay - 3 kind of modes ( endless, time challenge and sliding) - 11 Types of balls - Custom achievements HOW TO PLAY Swipe the ball towards the hoop to score. Collect stars to unlock new balls. Improve your skills and become the master of the hoop. Very Fun! Game for everybody!
